head: <!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><style>body {font-family: arial, sans-serif;max-width: 1200px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top: 0;}table {width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;text-align: left;border-width: 0;border-style: solid;border-color: grey;}tbody>tr {border-bottom: 1pt solid #dddddd;}th,td {padding: 8px;}th:first-child,td:first-child {padding-left: 16px;}th {border-color: #616161;background-color: #616161;color: white;}th:hover {background-color: #333333;}tr:hover td {background-color: #24a204;border-color: #24a204;color: white;}@media (max-width: 40em) {section {margin: 0;}}@media (min-width: 40em) {section {margin: 20px;}}@media print {tbody>tr {border-bottom: 1pt solid black;}table {border: 1pt solid black;}th {border-color: black;background-color: transparent;color: black;border-bottom: 1pt solid black;}}@media (max-width: 40em) {.searchbar {padding-top: 1rem;padding-bottom: 1rem;margin-bottom: 0;}}@media (min-width: 40em) {.searchbar {padding-top: 0.5rem;padding-bottom: 0.5rem;margin-bottom: 1rem;}}.searchbar {margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;padding-left: 1rem;padding-right: 0;border: 1px solid #ccc;width: calc(100% - 1rem - 2px);}input:focus {outline-width: 0;}@media print {.searchbar {display: none;}}tr:hover .button {background-color: #24a204;border-color: white;color: white;}th:nth-child(4),td:nth-child(4) {text-align: center;}.button {padding: 2px 4px;text-align: center;text-decoration: none;display: inline-block;margin: 4px 2px;-webkit-transition-duration: 0.4s;transition-duration: 0.4s;cursor: pointer;background-color: transparent;color: black;border: 2px solid #dddddd;border-radius: 6px;}.button:hover {border-color: white;background-color: white !important;color: #24a204 !important;}.label-container {position: fixed;bottom: 6%;right: calc(5% + 80px);display: table;visibility: hidden;}.label-text {color: #FFF;background: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.5);display: table-cell;vertical-align: middle;padding: 10px;border-radius: 3px;}.float {position: fixed;width: 60px;height: 60px;bottom: 5%;right: 5%;background-color: #06C;color: #FFF;border-radius: 50px;text-align: center;box-shadow: 2px 2px 3px #999;-webkit-transition-duration: 0.4s;transition-duration: 0.4s;}.float:hover {background-color: #0080ff;box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px 2px #999;}a.float+div.label-container {visibility: hidden;opacity: 0;transition: visibility 0s, opacity 0.5s ease;}a.float:hover+div.label-container {visibility: visible;opacity: 1;}</style><script src="w3.js"></script>
